{
  "stem": "2690.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But also, because we knew so many people, and we knew the head of the barrack, we said, can you do something to keep my dad from going to Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, yes, I will see to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother, after we were all gone, there was a friend of ours, she was from a mixed marriage, half Jewish, half-- her father was Jewish, her mother was Gentile.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She went to my mother and put my mother into hiding somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my mother got very sick there because she couldn't stand being away from her children and her husband.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That-- and then when we knew we would go to France, my sister went up to the head of the camp and said, we'll get my mother back here.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we quickly got hold of this Gentile girl and she got my mother back into the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we could send a letter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could send mail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband was making the roads.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had to work as a road worker, and I was doing-- tearing clothes apart because everything they could use.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later, my husband was a tailor and he had to repair the German, their wives' clothes or make them over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my daughter was walking around and then she got, my mother made her like a nurse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She made her a little apron from rags and, you know, like she was a Red Cross nurse.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was only a child, but the people did remember her very well because [INTERPOSING VOICES] she was such a beauty when she was little.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you were always afraid that you would be on the next transport going around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You never knew if you were not one of the 1,000 that would go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
